        <Title>PlatformKit</Title>
        <PackageReleaseNotes>## Changes since 2.4 series

### Additions
* Added new ``MacOsSystemInformation`` class to represent Mac System Profiler information.
* Re-added ``MacSystemProfilerDataType`` enum
* Added the interface for MacSystemDetection - The implementing class will be added in a future pre-release version
* Added in code documentation for ``MacProcessorType`` enum
* Added Mac Specific Enums ``MacDisplayType`` and ``MacDeviceFamily``
* Added Mac Models ``MacSupportStatus`` and ``MacModel`` to represent information regarding Mac products.
* Added Shared Model ``ReleaseYearModel`` and Shared Enum ``ReleaseYearTimeframe``


### Changes
* Clarified deprecation of ``RunCommand`` to suggest alternatives.
* Moved ``ShowLicenseInConsole`` method to ``ConsoleHelper`` class - A copy will remain in the PlatformManager class until PlatformKit V3
* Minor Tweaks

### Deprecations
* macOS 10.13 support has been deprecated and will throw an error in V5.
* Delayed deprecation of Windows 8.1 and Windows Server 2012 R2 support from V4 to V5.
* Deprecated ``RunActionOn`` method - This will be removed in V3 and will not be replaced.</PackageReleaseNotes>
